<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>13273</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18624</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>看到宫殿大门打开，马格里布笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18625</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24278</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“随便挑一盏新灯吧，小姐！”他说道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24279</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30133</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>贝德拉公主和她的仆人们从窗户往下看，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30134</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39981</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那个仆人挑了一盏崭新的闪闪发光的灯，然后把阿拉丁的灯给了魔法师。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39982</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>46458</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你一定是疯了，老人家。”仆人说着，关上了大门。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>46459</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51361</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>马格里布带着宝物急急忙忙地离开了，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51362</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57363</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他仍然能听见那些女人的笑声，但是他不在乎。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57364</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64742</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我终于拿到神灯了！”他大叫着，把剩下的新灯扔到沟里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64743</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>70473</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他跑呀跑，一直跑到城墙外一个安静的地方。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>70474</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74421</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，他开始摩擦神灯。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74422</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77881</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>精灵从烟雾中出现了，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77882</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86050</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>马格里布听见了一阵高扬神秘的音乐，他吃惊得坐了下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86051</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92333</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我来了，准备好为您服务，主人！”精灵说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92334</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96323</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，他仔细地看了看马格里布。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96324</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103365</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“您是谁？”他说，“我还以为是别人叫我呢。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103366</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107632</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我是马格里布。”魔法师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107633</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114632</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好吧，没关系。”精灵说。他把手臂放在胸前。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114633</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121860</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谁是神灯的主人，我就听谁的。告诉我您的愿望。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121861</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126744</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的愿望很简单。”马格里布小声说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126745</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132461</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“把我，还有阿拉丁的宫殿带到埃及去。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132462</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141165</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“闭上眼睛。”精灵说，“您张开眼睛的时候，就已经到那儿了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141166</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148688</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每天早上，苏丹王都喜欢从他的窗户向他女儿的宫殿望去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148689</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155786</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>今天早上，他往外望去，但是什么都没有了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155787</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162338</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他揉了揉眼睛，也眨了眨眼睛，但是还是什么都没有。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162339</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168778</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“宫殿在哪里？”国王大吼，“我女儿在哪里？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168779</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173012</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他死死地盯着宫殿原来的位置。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173013</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179979</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“首席大臣！”他大叫道。大臣急急忙忙地跑了过来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179980</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185054</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“过来这里。”苏丹王说，“你看见了什么？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185055</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192270</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“什么都没有，国王。”首席大臣说，“阿拉丁的宫殿消失了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192271</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>205243</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊，我女儿到哪里去了？”国王喊道。他开始哭泣。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>205244</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>214219</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我告诉过您。”首席大臣说，“我说过阿拉丁的宫殿是用魔法建造的！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>214220</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219463</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>国王震怒了：“阿拉丁在哪里？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>219464</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223826</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他去打猎了。”首席大臣说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223827</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>231092</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“马上带他来见我！”国王大吼，“我要把他的头剁下来！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>231093</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>236477</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>太阳落山之前，国王的军队抓到了阿拉丁。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>236478</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>241176</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他被绑在锁链上，拖着回城。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>241177</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>245932</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>国王的两个守卫把阿拉丁带回了城堡。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>245933</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>251621</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>国王和首席大臣进来的时候，他们强迫阿拉丁跪下。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>251622</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>263723</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>国王的眼睛哭得又红又肿，首席大臣对着阿拉丁轻蔑地笑了笑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>263724</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>269257</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我犯了什么罪，伟大的国王？”阿拉丁大声问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>269258</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>274850</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你用魔法把我的女儿偷走了！”国王大喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>274851</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>279015</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“还有她的宫殿！”首席大臣补充说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>279016</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>283101</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不明白。”阿拉丁说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>283102</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>287721</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那我就给你看。”苏丹王说，“过来！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>287722</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>292799</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>守卫把阿拉丁提了起来，拖着他走过大厅，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>292799</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>298199</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>走进了国王的卧室，来到了窗户跟前。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>298200</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>304378</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“看！你的宫殿还有我的女儿在哪儿？”国王问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>304379</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>309489</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿拉丁朝外望去，发现空无一物。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>309490</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>314666</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这不是我干的。”阿拉丁说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>314667</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>322757</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是请给我40天时间，我会找到公主，并把她给您带回来。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>322758</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>325747</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>国王流着泪答应了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>325748</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>336949</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是如果你不回来，我会找到你，然后杀了你！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>